Package: openmediavault-uartdisplay
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, python3-serial, systemd, btrfs-progs, mdadm, util-linux
Description: UART Display Daemon for NAS Status
 This package provides a daemon service that monitors NAS storage arrays
 (mdadm or btrfs) and displays status information on an embedded UART display.
 .
 Features:
  - Monitors mdadm RAID arrays
  - Monitors btrfs multi-device filesystems
  - Displays used/total space and array status
  - System statistics (CPU, Memory, Temperature, Uptime)
  - Network interface information with traffic speed
  - Configurable via /etc/openmediavault/uartdisplay.conf
  - 10-second update interval (configurable)
